creator: Ngân hàng Bản Việt
descriptionHtml:
Viet Capital Mobile Banking offers you the safer and simple way to:
- Check your account balances
- View your transaction history
- Conduct instant funds transfer
- Locate ATMs, branches and promotion spots close to you
- Pay bills
- Check exchange rates, interest rates, personal deposit, loan calculator
Simply log in using your existing Internet Banking account information. Do not have Internet Banking account? Please visit our branches to apply.
For further information, please visit our website at www.vietcapitalbank.com.vn
Banking at your fingertips!
